📚 Smart Online Bookstore Interface

This project is a responsive and interactive online bookstore developed using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. It allows users to browse books with pagination, add items to cart and wishlist, and stores user selections using localStorage for a better user experience.

✨ Features:

- Dynamic book listing with images and prices
- Add to Cart & Wishlist functionality
- Real-time cart and wishlist count updates
- Pagination for easy navigation
- Persistent data using browser localStorage

